This paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category as it deals with reinforcement learning methods. It also involves privacy concerns (cs.CR) as it aims to protect sensitive data. Additionally, it involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it presents a differentially private approach for off-policy evaluation. The paper also involves data structures (cs.DS) as it deals with the manipulation of data, and cybersecurity (cs.CY) as it aims to protect sensitive information.
